POWER OUTAGES
Steps to follow:
v Check your fuses and breakers, to ensure the problem is not within your electrical system.
v Report the outage immediately if you have determined the outage is on LREMC's system by calling
our toll-free number at the top of the page, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.
V Always stay away from downed power lines.
V For up-to-date outage information, please visit our outage map at http://outages.lumbeeriver.com/
811
SAFETY TIP
If you have underground electric lines, never start a digging project without knowing where the lines are
located. Call 811 before you dig to avoid serious injury, expenses or possible penalties. Call at least 48
hours before you dig. An expert will come to your home and mark the location of any utility lines.

PAYMENT OPTIONS (Check, Visa, MasterCard & Cash Accepted)
1. Pay Online: PAY NOW at www.lumbeeriver.com
2. Pay Mobile: Download the SmartHub app @ www.lumbeeriver.com

4. Pay by Mail: Enclose your payment in the courtesy return envelope provided in your bill

monthly bill and Lumbee River EMC will draft the amount of your bill from your bank account on the
